# Ignore attemptX directories

- Treat any directory named `attempt` followed by one or more digits as excluded from all work.
- Do not read, search, edit, refactor, or propose changes for files inside these paths.
- Skip these directories even when they appear nested at any depth.

Examples:
- `attempt1/`
- `attempt2/`
- `attempt10/`
- `src/attempt3/feature.ts`
- `foo/bar/attempt99/baz.txt`

Match intent:
- Directory name pattern: `attempt[0-9]+`
